- *Amazon Lex V2* â€” Conversational AI
- *AWS Lambda (Python)* â€” Custom slot validation logic
- *Kommunicate.io* â€” Frontend chatbot deployment
- *AWS IAM Roles* â€” Secure service access
- *AWS Management Console* â€” Bot and Lambda management

